    {
      "text": "Where the Wild Things Are is a platform-adventure video game released in 2009. It is based on the movie of the same name, released the same day. The game is available for PlayStation 3, Wii and Xbox 360 as well as Nintendo DS. It was developed by Griptonite Games, except for the Nintendo DS, which was developed by WayForward Technologies. All versions were published by Warner Bros. Games.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    },
    {
      "text": "『Where the Wild Things Are』は、2009年にリリースされたプラットフォームアドベンチャービデオゲームです。同日公開された同名の映画を原作としています。本ゲームは、PlayStation 3、Wii、Xbox 360に加え、Nintendo DSでもプレイ可能です。Nintendo DS版を除く全バージョンはGriptonite Gamesが開発し、Nintendo DS版はWayForward Technologiesが開発しました。全バージョンはWarner Bros. Gamesによって発売されました。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "ai_local_gemma4",
      "base_lang": "en"
    }
